<link>https://the-decoder.com/apollo-economist-warns-ai-profit-gains-outside-tech-could-take-well-beyond-what-wall-street-expects/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://the-decoder.com/?p=37446</guid>
<pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 10:28:57 +0000</pubDate>
<source>the-decoder.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【the-decoder.com】阿波罗首席经济学家托尔斯滕·斯洛克认为，科技行业之外不会出现由AI驱动的利润率增长。在医疗、银行或制药等受监管行业中，流程改革和隐私规则可能将生产力提升推迟数年。如果这一过程需要五年而非五个月，许多AI股票将面临痛苦的重新定价。本文《阿波罗经济学家警告：科技领域之外的AI利润增长可能“远超”华尔街预期》最初发表于The Decoder。<br/><br/><a href="https://the-decoder.com/apollo-economist-warns-ai-profit-gains-outside-tech-could-take-well-beyond-what-wall-street-expects/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
